:RebelYell:

 RebelYell had been flying for several hours when off
in the distance he spotted a ship."Must be it" he
thought.As he got closer he saw a bot sitting at the
entrance.When he landed he dropped the parts he had
been carrying on the ground."I'm RebelYell," he said.
"Now could somebody tell me what the hell is goin' on
on this slaggin' rock??"
